 \"Directories created\"","description":"Create all task group directories"}},{"tool_name":"Bash","tool_use_id":"toolu_014QS6Q2G7RXZd7snJmXhdc8","tool_input":{"command":"mkdir -p \"/Users/anjan/workspace/projects/ai/ai-sdd/ai-sdd-claude/specs/photocop/specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-01-infrastructure-scaffold\" \"/Users/anjan/workspace/projects/ai/ai-sdd/ai-sdd-claude/specs/photocop/specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-02-backend-analysis-pipeline\" \"/Users/anjan/workspace/projects/ai/ai-sdd/ai-sdd-claude/specs/photocop/specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-03-backend-api-output\" \"/Users/anjan/workspace/projects/ai/ai-sdd/ai-sdd-claude/specs/photocop/specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-04-frontend\" \"/Users/anjan/workspace/projects/ai/ai-sdd/ai-sdd-claude/specs/photocop/specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-05-integration-qa\" && echo \"done\"","description":"Create task group directories"}},{"tool_name":"Bash","tool_use_id":"toolu_01L98ihKCDb1Q25PEm6wwRZT","tool_input":{"command":"mkdir -p specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-01-infrastructure-scaffold specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-02-backend-analysis-pipeline specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-03-backend-api-output specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-04-frontend specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-05-integration-qa && echo \"done\"","description":"Create task group directories from project root"}},{"tool_name":"Bash","tool_use_id":"toolu_01FRhNxMyTqA8AXpQH17j4hw","tool_input":{"command":"mkdir -p specs/plan-tasks/tasks/TG-01-infrastructure-scaffold && echo \"done\"","description":"Create first task group directory with cd"}},{"tool_name":"Write","tool_use_id":"toolu_01SnQWJvFLPTv1qB7WpR4A3R","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/anjan/workspace/projects/ai/ai-sdd/ai-sdd-claude/specs/photocop/specs/plan-tasks/plan.md","content":"# Task Breakdown — PhotoCop\n\n## Summary\n- Task groups: 5 (Jira Epics)\n- Total tasks: 18 leaf tasks (no subtasks)\n- Estimated effort: 8–10 days (parallel, 3–4 devs) / 22–30 days (sequential)\n- Critical path: T-001 → T-002 → T-003 → T-004 → T-007 → T-008 → T-011 → T-012 → T-018\n\n## Contents\n- [tasks/index.md](tasks/index.md) — all task groups\n\n## Critical path\n\nThe longest dependency chain runs through TG-01 (project scaffold), TG-02 (analysis pipeline), and TG-03 (API and output):\n\n- **T-001** (project setup) must complete before any backend or frontend work begins.\n- **T-002** (backend config) gates every backend module that imports `Settings`.\n- **T-003** (image ingestion) is the gateway into the pipeline; all analyser tasks depend on it.\n- **T-004, T-005, T-006** (analysers) may run in parallel; all must complete before T-007.\n- **T-007** (score aggregator) feeds T-008 (analysis engine).\n- **T-008** (analysis engine orchestrator) feeds T-009, T-010, T-011 (parallel output tasks).\n- **T-011** (response assembler) feeds T-012 (FastAPI router).\n- **T-012** (router) is a prerequisite for frontend integration and E2E tests (T-018).\n\nFull critical path: **T-001 → T-002 → T-003 → T-004 → T-007 → T-008 → T-011 → T-012 → T-018**\n\n## Key risks\n\n1. **T-004 (ELA Analyser) — HIGH**: JPEG re-save quality variations across Pillow versions produce non-deterministic ELA maps; must pin library version and validate against known fixtures.\n2. **T-006 (Clone Detector) — HIGH**: ORB descriptor matching is CPU-intensive; may breach the 10 s performance budget for large images. Requires early benchmarking.\n3. **T-008 (Analysis Engine) — HIGH**: `asyncio` + `ThreadPoolExecutor` fanout; incorrect isolation can cause image mutation across analysers. Thread-safety must be verified via tests.\n4. **T-002 (Backend Config) — MEDIUM**: `python-magic` depends on libmagic C library; missing OS package causes hard startup failure.\n5. **T-018 (E2E Tests) — MEDIUM**: Full pipeline tests require Docker Compose stack; CI must support Docker-in-Docker or equivalent.\n\n## Security blockers\n\nNo `specs/security-design-review.md` exists for this project. Security constraints derive from `constitution.md`:\n\n- All uploads validated via magic-byte check before decoding (T-002, T-003).\n- No image bytes, derived data, or EXIF values written to disk or logs (T-003, T-009, T-010).\n- No secrets in source code; environment variables only (T-001, T-002).\n- CORS origins configurable via environment variable (T-012).\n"}},{"tool_name":"Write","tool_use_id":"toolu_01RkCF7URQ4qmrsScFnPquTE","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/anjan/workspace/projects/ai/ai-sdd/ai-sdd-claude/specs/photocop/specs/plan-tasks/tasks/index.md","content":"# Implementation Tasks\n\n| Group | Title | Tasks | Total Effort | Status |\n|-------|-------|-------|-------------|--------|\n| [TG-01](TG-01-infrastructure-scaffold/index.md) | Infrastructure & Scaffold | 2 tasks | ~2 days | PENDING |\n| [TG-02](TG-02-backend-analysis-pipeline/index.md) | Backend Analysis Pipeline | 7 tasks | ~12 days | PENDING |\n| [TG-03](TG-03-backend-api-output/index.md) | Backend API & Output | 4 tasks | ~6 days | PENDING |\n| [TG-04](TG-04-frontend/index.md) | Frontend | 4 tasks | ~6 days | PENDING |\n| [TG-05](TG-05-integration-qa/index.md) | Integration & QA | 1 task | ~2 days | PENDING |\n"}},{"tool_name":"Write","tool_use_id":"toolu_01FAM3NxXRQe6Me2fciatNgM","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/anjan/workspace/projects/ai/ai-sdd/ai-sdd-claude/specs/photocop/specs/plan-tasks/tasks/index.md","content":"# Implementation Tasks\n\n| Group | Title | Tasks | Total Effort | Status |\n|-------|-------|-------|-------------|--------|\n| [TG-01](TG-01-infrastructure-scaffold/index.md) | Infrastructure & Scaffold | 2 tasks | ~2 days | PENDING |\n| [TG-02](TG-02-backend-analysis-pipeline/index.md) | Backend Analysis Pipeline | 7 tasks | ~12 days | PENDING |\n| [TG-03](TG-03-backend-api-output/index.md) | Backend API & Output | 4 tasks | ~6 days | PENDING |\n| [TG-04](TG-04-frontend/index.md) | Frontend | 4 tasks | ~6 days | PENDING |\n| [TG-05](TG-05-integration-qa/index.md) | Integration & QA | 1 task | ~2 days | PENDING |\n"}},{"tool_name":"Write","tool_use_id":"toolu_017rGDn946Quj